2012 Sparkle Emma Posthumous release.

[90] Houston's first film role was in The Bodyguard , released in 1992 and co-starring Kevin Costner .

Houston played Rachel Marron, a star who is stalked by a crazed fan and hires a bodyguard to protect her.

[92] Houston's mainstream appeal allowed people to look at the movie color-blind.

